### 1、获取传感器列表
POST https://www.zhtk-iot.com:8543/api/DataProvision/sensorList
Authorization: {{loginToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pagesize": "10",
  "curpagenum": "1",
  "snAddress": "",
  "tpCode": "",
  "devState": "",
  "sortMode": "desc"
}

